---
title: Meatloaves with Creamy Thyme Sauce plus Garlic Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: This delicious dish is the definition of umami. Not sure if you’ve ever experienced the “fifth taste?” After one bite, you’ll totally understand the obsession. Mini meatloaves are baked to perfection, then draped in a supremely savory thyme sauce. The luxurious loaves are served alongside crispy roasted Brussels sprouts and garlicky mashed potatoes—aka more things to catch any runaway sauce. Plus, the whole shebang cooks up in a flash (just 35 minutes!). What are you waiting for?
